## Summary

Deep PI SDK integration — promotes `pi-ai` and `pi-tui` to direct dependencies, wires agent events from per-task sessions, and builds TUI overlay infrastructure with persistent dashboards.

### Slices Delivered (6/6)

| Slice | Title | PR |
|-------|-------|----|
| M06-S01 | pi-ai Direct Dependency + Type Cleanup | #40 |
| M06-S02 | Agent Event Deepening | #41 |
| M06-S03 | pi-tui Foundation | #42 |
| M06-S04 | Status Dashboard Overlay | #43 |
| M06-S05 | Workflow Visualizer Overlay | #44 |
| M06-S06 | Execution Monitor Overlay | #45 |

### Key Changes

- **pi-ai/pi-tui promoted** to direct dependencies; type aliases cleaned up
- **AgentEventPort** with 8 typed events (`turn_start`, `turn_end`, `message_update`, `tool_execution_start/end`, etc.)
- **Per-turn metrics** in AgentResult via TurnMetricsCollector
- **OverlayDataPort** for read-only domain state queries
- **3 TUI overlays**: Status Dashboard (`ctrl+alt+d`), Workflow Visualizer (`ctrl+alt+w`), Execution Monitor (`ctrl+alt+e`)
- **Shared PiAgentDispatchAdapter** wires all agent events through a single hub

### Stats

- 65 files changed, +3884 -388
- 7 squash-merged slice PRs
- All 1718 tests passing

## Test plan

- [x] `npx vitest run` — 1718/1718 pass
- [x] All 6 slice PRs individually reviewed (spec + code + security)
- [x] Milestone audit: 6/6 requirements validated
- [ ] Manual: verify overlays render correctly in TUI
EOF
